Description: 'mappestRisk' has three different modules: (1) model fitting & selection
             using a set of the most commonly used equations describing developmental 
             responses to temperature helped by already existing R packages 
             using equation helpers from rTPC(Padfield and O’Sullivan 2023),
             with visualization of model predictions to guide ecological criteria for
             model selection; (2) calculation of suitability thermal limits,
             which consist on a temperature interval delimiting the optimal 
             performance zone or suitability; and (3) climatic data extraction 
             & visualization with either exportable rasters, static map images
             or html, interactive maps.
